original_title: Hank and Lank: They Dude Up Some
overview: Hank and Lank have experienced a little rough weather since we last saw them and the fact that they are disreputably clothed has not been overlooked by them. They need something new. But how? After some thought Hank's cheerful countenance lightens. He goes on to explain his little scheme in detail.
title: Hank and Lank: They Dude Up Some
